sentence: Among the underlying components of the Russell 3000 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in Caesarstone Ltd (Symbol: CSTE), where a total of 1,135 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 113,500 underlying shares.
That amounts to about 47.1% of CSTE's average daily trading volume over the past month of 241,200 shares.
Especially high volume was seen for the $12.50 strike put option expiring July 19, 2019 , with 1,125 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 112,500 underlying shares of CSTE.

Home Depot Inc (Symbol: HD) saw options trading volume of 30,024 contracts, representing approximately 3.0 million underlying shares or approximately 46.9% of HD's average daily trading volume over the past month, of 6.4 million shares.

Particularly high volume was seen for the $172.50 strike call option expiring November 23, 2018 , with 2,673 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 267,300 underlying shares of HD.

Particularly high volume was seen for the $70 strike call option expiring December 21, 2018 , with 2,010 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 201,000 underlying shares of GBT.
